\c 17
\p
\v 1 Usabaira Jehovha Mwari wako nzombe kana gwai pariri pane chipomerwa, chipi nechipi chakaipa, nokuti chinyangadzo kuna Jehovha Mwari wako\x + Rev. 22.20.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Kana kukawanikwa pakati pako, mukati meripi neripi remasuwo ako Jehovha Mwari wako aanokupa, murume kana mukadzi wakaita zvakaipa pameso aJehovha Mwari wako\x + 17.7. 13.6-14.\x*, pakudarika sungano yake\x + Josh. 7.11,15. 23.16. Vato. 2.20. 2 Madz. 18.12. Hos. 6.7. 8.1.\x*,
\v 3 ndokuenda ndokushumira vamwe vamwari, ndokuvanamata, kana zuva, kana mwedzi, kana hondo ipi neipi yekumatenga\x + 4.19.\x*, chandisina kuraira\x + Jer. 7.31. 19.5. 32.35.\x*;
\v 4 zvino zvikaudzwa kwauri, zvino ukanzwa ndokubvunzisisa, zvino tarira, ichokwadi, chinhu chechokwadi, chinyangadzo ichi chakaitwa kwaIsraeri\x + 13.14.\x*;
\v 5 ipapo uchabudisa murume uyo kana mukadzi uyo vakaita chinhu icho chakaipa kumasuwo ako, murume kana mukadzi; zvino uchavataka nemabwe vagofa\x + Rev. 24.14,16. Josh. 7.25.\x*.
\v 6 Nemuromo wezvapupu zviviri, kana zvapupu zvitatu, uyo wakafanira kufa achaurawa; haangaurawi nemuromo wechapupu chimwe\x + Num.. 35.30. Joh. 8.17.\x*.
\v 7 Ruoko rwezvapupu rwuchatanga kuva pamusoro pake kumuuraya, zvino pashure ruoko rwevanhu vese\x + 13.9; Mab. 7.58.\x*. Saizvozvo uchabvisa chakaipa kubva pakati pako\x + 17.12. 13.5.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Kana pane nyaya yakarema kwazvo kwauri, pamutongo\x + 19.17. 21.5. 2 Makor. 19.8,10. Map. 122.5. Jer. 18.18. Hag. 2.11. Mara. 2.7.\x*, pakati peropa neropa, pakati pekuenzanisira nekuenzanisira, uye pakati pekurova nekurova, dziri nyaya dzekupikisana mukati memasuwo ako, ipapo uchasimuka\x + 19.17. 21.5. 2 Makor. 19.8,10. Map. 122.5. Jer. 18.18. Hag. 2.11. Mara. 2.7.\x* ndokukwira kunzvimbo Jehovha Mwari wako yaachasarudza\x + 12.5.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino uchauya kuvapristi VaRevhi\x + 19.17. 21.5. 2 Makor. 19.8,10. Map. 122.5. Jer. 18.18. Hag. 2.11. Mara. 2.7.\x*, nekumutongi achavapo pamazuva iwawo, ugobvunza\x + 19.17. 21.5. 2 Makor. 19.8,10. Map. 122.5. Jer. 18.18. Hag. 2.11. Mara. 2.7.\x*; zvino vachakuudza murango wemutongo\x + Eze. 44.24.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino uchaita zvinoenderana nemurango wavachakuudza kubva panzvimbo iyo Jehovha yaachasarudza; zvino uchachengeta kuti uite zvinoenderana nezvose zvavanokudzidzisa.
\v 11 Uchaita zvichienderana nemurango wemurairo wavachakudzidzisa, uye zvichienderana nemutongo wavachakuudza; haungatsaukiri kurudyi kana kuruboshwe kubva pashoko ravanotaura kwauri.
\v 12 Nemunhu unoita nekuzvikudza kuti asateerera kumupristi\x + 17.13. Det. 1.43. 18.20,22. Ezi. 10.8.\x* amire kushumirapo Jehovha Mwari wako\x + 10.8. 18.5,7.\x*, kana kumutongi, munhu uyo achafa; uye iwe uchabvisa chakaipa kubva pana Israeri\x + 13.5.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino vanhu vese vachazvinzwa ndokutya, vakasazozvikudzazve\x + 13.11.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Paunosvika munyika Jehovha Mwari wako yaanokupa, ndokuigara nhaka, ndokugara mairi, zvino uchati: Ndichazviisira mambo semarudzi ese akandipoteredza\x + 1 Zvak. 8.5,19,20.\x*;
\v 15 u\add mu\add*ise kwazvo ave mambo pamusoro pako, iye Jehovha Mwari wako waachasarudza. Achibva pakati\x + 1 Zvak. 9.15. 10.24. 16.12. 1 Makor. 22.10.\x* pehama dzenyu u\add mu\add*ise ave mambo pamusoro pako\x + Jer. 30.21.\x*. Haugoni kuisa kuva mweni pamusoro pako asiri hama yako.
\v 16 Asi asazviwanzira mabhiza\x + 1 Madz. 4.26. 10.26,28. 2 Makor. 1.16. 9.28.\x*, kana kudzoseresa vanhu kuEgipita, kuti awanze mabhiza\x + Isa. 31.1. Eze. 17.15.\x*, Jehovha sezvaakati kwamuri: Hamungadzokerizve nenzira iyo\x + 28.68; Hos. 11.5; Eki. 13.17; Num.. 14.3,4; Jer. 42.15-19.\x*.
\v 17 Uye asazviwanzira vakadzi, kuti moyo wake usatsauka; uye asazviwanzira zvikuru sirivha negoridhe\x + 1 Madz. 11.3,4.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino zvichava paanogara pachigaro cheumambo hwake, kuti achazvinyorera dzokororo yemurairo\x + 2 Madz. 11.12.\x* uyu mubhuku, unobva pazviri pamberi\x + 31.9,26. 2 Madz. 22.8. 2 Makor. 34.14.\x* pevapristi VaRevhi\x + 17.9. Det. 18.1. 24.8. 27.9. Josh. 3.3. 8.33.\x*.
\v 19 Richava naye, uye achaverenga mariri mazuva ese eupenyu hwake\x + Josh. 1.8.\x*, kuti adzidze kutya Jehovha Mwari wake, kuchengeta mashoko ese emurairo uyu nezvimiso izvi, kuti azviite\x + 4.10; 14.23.\x*;
\v 20 kuti moyo wake usazvikudza pamusoro pehama dzake, uye kuti asatsauka pamurairo \add kuenda\add* kurudyi kana kuruboshwe\x + 5.32. 1 Madz. 15.5.\x*; kuti arebese mazuva paumambo hwake, iye nevana vake, pakati paIsraeri\x + 4.40.\x*.